print("All test cases pass.solution(stdin: str) -> str:
    n = int(stdin.split("\n")[0])
    a = list(map(int, stdin.split("\n")[1].split()))

    left, right = 0, n - 1
    result = []
    k = 0

    for i in range(n):
        if left < right and a[left] < a[right]:
            result.append("L")
            k += 1
            left += 1
        else:
            result.append("R")
            k += 1
            right -= 1

    return str(k) + "\n" + "".join(result)

    n, k = map(int, stdin.readline().split())
    messages = list(map(int, stdin.readline().split()))

    conversations = []
    for i in range(n):
        friend_id = messages[i]
        if friend_id in conversations:
            continue
        elif len(conversations) < k:
            conversations.append(friend_id)
        else:
            conversations.pop(k-1)
            conversations.insert(0, friend_id)

    return f"{len(conversations)}\n{' '.join(map(str, conversations))}\n"
